.TH PERROR 1
.SH NAME
perror \- print the error message from a error number
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B perror [OPTIONS] <errno>
.SH DESCRIPTION
perror prints a friendly error message from an error number

-h Print help

-v Print version

-n Also print number with the string

.SH EXAMPLES
$ perror 4

Interrupted system call

